Name: Tap Those Targets
About the game: Can you tap them all? Casual target gallery! Click as many targets as you can, but don't miss or you'll lose a life! THREE WAYS TO PLAY: Normal - Three lives, it gets tougher and tougher! One Life - One life, shrinking targets, how many can you click? Fast Fingers - Click as many times as you can in ten seconds!
